1.0.name: wordpress/mysense1
1.0.description: An original responsive theme suitable for any device and resolution. The theme includes three widget areas in the footer, one at the side and two on the top, with a slide on the top that is enabled with a check button in the post edit. In the home page, the post is displayed with only the title, image and eventual subtitle. Yuo can choose if display the logo of the site or a simple site name and site description.
